sudo mount -t cifs //192.168.1.122/fortomato test_mnt/ -o username=robin,password=abc123
sudo mount.cifs -v //LATLOGIC/code ~/share -o 'username=robin.chew,password=abc123,domain=lwa.local,uid=robin'

Troubleshoot
############

failed: No such device::

    insmod /path/to/cifs.ko

Invalid Argument::

    append '-o username=guest'
